{
  "stem": "24614.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- but he still had enough to go to one of his friends, non-Jewish friends, at night to exchange diamonds.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He still had some diamonds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And when he got to his friend, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the friend decided that he wants the diamonds, but he doesn't want to pay for it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So instead of taking away the diamonds when my daddy slept over there, he gassed my daddy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] The next day--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day, a police who worked for the underground came to tell us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother took my daddy's prayer shawl [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] and told the police to make sure that he is buried with that, that he's put-- that it's put around him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could not go to the funeral.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because if we would have gone to the funeral, then we would have been killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What he told us is that the casket will be in a truck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he can make sure that the truck should go through the house where we are hiding so that we can see the casket.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're all saying we saw the casket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I guess I did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My daddy was buried in the cemetery, in a Christian cemetery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My mother [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] said after years of liberation that she cannot die if she doesn't rebury my daddy in a Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When my son was-- I don't know-- younger-- that must've been six or eight years old, my husband, my son, my mother went to Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we reburied my daddy in a Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now Antwerp doesn't have-- Belgium doesn't have Jewish cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It has a no man's land between Holland and Belgium.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
